text: Tsvetanka Rangelova (born 31 August 1938) is a Bulgarian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Haskovo Province
